title: Wrist Diamonds
summary: Wrist Diamonds provides digital diamonds for Android Wear watches.
description: Wrist Diamonds offers high quality digital diamonds around the face of your watch. The diamond dial "blings" when the movable background randomly moves behind the diamond, giving your watch a high class look. There are 8 different color diamonds, and 1 mix and match version to pick from. Please download and share with others.
